_sText:
This is my first map.

It has been released on Teh MadHouse and now i felt i could release it to all who want to test it.

Original idea had some more stuff added, but this is the final release version.

I want to thank Teh Madhouse Community for making this possible and to all who helped testing it, for putting up with me everyday and being there when needed.
I love you all guys!!! :D

Big thanks goes to Robtronic for the optimization tips and the Monitors that weren't used in the final version (Thank you anyway mate :) ).

Credit also goes to Chrazini for the letter prefab he made available here on FPSB, these ones are very sexy ;)

It was made for the Community I represent, that gives me lots of fun hours and support (and sometimes when teh pwning gets hard hates my guts... :D ) and hope more will follow.

Visit us on www.tehmadhouse.com/portal if you feel like it :D

Please leave your assessment, as its my first map and mappers need feedback.

Behave!

VoGon
